title: Coronavirus, a year later...
itunes:title: Coronavirus, a year later...
itunes:subtitle: A Podcast from your favorite homeboy
description:
What up peeps! Here is a good episode for your Good Friday! 

Listen in as Drew, Eric, and Napoleon discuss coronavirus a year later, Derrick Jaxson, and "Asian Hate". 

Share your thoughts with us on our Facebook page https://www.facebook.com/MyHomeboyPodcast
Also a big shout out to our homies over at Castro for putting a real podcast on their discovery page!
